      <title>俄罗斯致命袭击引发极端暴力浪潮担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/deadly-attack-in-russia-stirs-fear-of-wave-of-extremist-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫斯科音乐厅遭袭数月后，穆斯林聚居区达吉斯坦又发生致命枪击，这引发人们担忧俄罗斯可能正面临宗教极端分子的暴力浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/deadly-attack-in-russia-stirs-fear-of-wave-of-extremist-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:56:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟绕过奥尔班否决，支持俄罗斯为乌克兰提供资产利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/eu-backs-russian-asset-profits-for-ukraine-by-dodging-orban-veto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在找到绕过匈牙利否决权的方法后，欧盟成员国同意从冻结俄罗斯资产的暴利中向乌克兰提供 14 亿欧元（15 亿美元）的军事援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/eu-backs-russian-asset-profits-for-ukraine-by-dodging-orban-veto</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国为德国汽车制造商提供优惠政策以避免缴纳电动汽车税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/china-floats-perks-for-german-carmakers-in-bid-to-stop-ev-levies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京方面表示，如果柏林方面能够说服欧盟取消对中国电动汽车出口征收的关税，德国的豪华汽车制造商将从中受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/china-floats-perks-for-german-carmakers-in-bid-to-stop-ev-levies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:36:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IFS 警告称，英国选民在税收和支出方面存在“知识真空”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/uk-voters-in-knowledge-vacuum-on-tax-and-spending-ifs-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政研究所警告称，在工党和保守党“回避”如何在不加税的情况下兑现支出承诺的艰难选择后，英国公众正在“在知识真空中投票”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/uk-voters-in-knowledge-vacuum-on-tax-and-spending-ifs-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:21:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯召见美国特使 讨论乌克兰对克里米亚发动导弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/russia-summons-us-envoy-over-ukraine-missile-strike-in-crimea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯外交部召见美国大使琳恩·特蕾西，就乌克兰对占领的克里米亚半岛的袭击进行讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/russia-summons-us-envoy-over-ukraine-missile-strike-in-crimea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:17:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>移民问题凸显对瑞士外籍劳工的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/switzerland-told-it-needs-foreign-workers-as-country-debates-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在围绕移民和欧盟人员自由流动的政治斗争中，瑞士政府发布的一份报告显示，瑞士企业因能够轻松聘用外国工人而受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/switzerland-told-it-needs-foreign-workers-as-country-debates-immigration</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚国王和总理安瓦尔受到恐怖威胁 引发逮捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/terror-threat-to-malaysia-king-and-prime-minister-sparks-arrests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚当局经调查发现有八人涉嫌对总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣和马来西亚国王发出恐怖主义威胁，随后逮捕了他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/terror-threat-to-malaysia-king-and-prime-minister-sparks-arrests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，博彩纠纷导致保守党支持率跌至新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-tories-hit-new-low-amid-betting-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博英国民意调查显示，里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的执政党保守党的支持率创下新低，有消息称，首相的几名亲密助手因在大选宣布之前对选举日期进行押注而受到调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-tories-hit-new-low-amid-betting-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:02:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
